Class ZeissCZIReaderX

  • java.lang.Object
    • loci.formats.FormatHandler
      • loci.formats.FormatReader
        • czireader.ZeissCZIReaderX
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, loci.formats.IFormatHandler, loci.formats.IFormatReader, loci.formats.IMetadataConfigurable, loci.formats.IPyramidHandler

    public class ZeissCZIReaderX
extends loci.formats.FormatReader
    ZeissCZIReaderX is the file format reader for Zeiss .czi files. This is a modified version of ZeissCZIReader from BioFormats 6.0.1
